The paper focuses on utilizing Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Artificial Intelligence (AI) to automatically generate answers to Alzheimer's Disease (AD)-related consumer questions posted by caregivers. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with NLP. The paper also involves the use of AI models, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (IR) as it aims to search for relevant questions and answers in online communities. This makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning (ML) techniques, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the use of social media websites, which falls under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
